    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a knob of <strong>butter alternative</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once melted, add most of the <strong>sliced onion</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 8-10 min or until softened and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
