    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cauliflower[s]</strong> into small florets</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1627402556042-x200.jpg",
