    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> and <strong>cucumber[s]</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>diced</strong> <strong>tomato</strong>, <strong>diced</strong> <strong>cucumber </strong>and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sliced onion</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> just before serving – this is your <strong>kachumber</strong></p>",
